[SN]TITLE[SN]
Vegetable farmers urged to form co-operative to lobby supermarkets

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Commercial vegetable growers have been urged to band together to have greater influence with the supermarkets.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
3 May 2016 Last updated at 19:53 BST
Selling to the bigger buyers can be difficult and unpredictable.
BBC News NI's agriculture correspondent Conor Macauley visited a farm to see the problems first hand.
